description:
Whether you’re connecting with your community for an upcoming activity or working with teammates on a project, Microsoft Teams helps bring people together so that they can get things done. It’s the only app that has communities, events, chats, channels, meetings, storage, tasks, and calendars in one place—so you can easily connect and manage access to information. Get your community, family, friends, or workmates together to accomplish tasks, share ideas, and make plans. Join audio and video calls in a secure setting, collaborate in documents, and store files and photos with built-in cloud storage. You can do it all in Microsoft Teams. 

Easily connect with anyone: 
• Skype is now part of Teams. Continue where you left off with your chats, calls and contacts in Microsoft Teams Free. 
• Meet securely with communities, teammates, family, or friends.
• Set up a meeting within seconds and invite anyone by sharing a link or calendar invite. 
• Chat 1-1 or to your entire community, @mention people in chats to get their attention. 
• Create a dedicated community to discuss specific topics and make plans*.
• Work closely and collaborate by keeping conversations organized by specific topics and projects with teams and channels.
• Video or audio call anyone directly in Teams or instantly convert a group chat to a call. 
• Use GIFs, emojis, and message animations to express yourself when words aren’t enough.
 
Accomplish plans and projects together: 
• Send photos and videos in chats to quickly and easily share important moments.
• Use cloud storage to access shared documents and files on the go. 
• Organize shared content in a community — events, photos, links, files —so you don’t have to waste time searching*. 
• Get the most out of your meetings by using screen share, whiteboard, or breakout in virtual rooms.
• Manage access to information and ensure the right people have access to the right info, even when people join and leave projects.
• Use task lists to stay on top of projects and plans - assign tasks, set due dates, and cross off items to keep everyone on the same page. 

Designed to give you peace of mind: 
• Securely collaborate with others while maintaining control over your data.
• Keep communities safe by allowing owners to remove inappropriate content or members*.
• Enterprise-level security and compliance you expect from Microsoft 365**. 

*Available when using Microsoft Teams with your Microsoft account.

**Commercial features of this app require a paid Microsoft 365 commercial subscription or a trial subscription of Microsoft Teams for work. If you’re not sure about your company’s subscription or the services you have access to, visit Office.com/Teams to learn more or contact your IT department. 

By downloading Teams, you agree to the license (see aka.ms/eulateamsmobile) and privacy terms (see aka.ms/privacy). For support or feedback, email us at mtiosapp@microsoft.com. EU Contract Summary: aka.ms/EUContractSummary

Consumer Health Data Privacy Policy   
https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2259814

BALTIC PETROLEUM degalinių tinklas  pristato – mobiliąją programėlę, patogiai Jūsų kelionei. Naudodamiesi mobiliąja programėle, lengvai rasite artimiausią BALTIC PETROLEUM degalinę. Programėlėje matysite specialią degalų kaina Jums artimiausioje degalinėje,  programėle galėsite atsiskaityti už degalus ar įsigytas prekes, matysite pirkimų istoriją ir degalinėje vykstančias akcijas ar patrauklius pasiūlymus. 

PATOGIAI IR GREITAI
Jei skubate ir degalinėje įsigijote tik degalų, apmokėti galite sėdėdami savo automobilyje BALTIC PETROLEUM mobiliąja programėle.

PARSISIŲSK IR ATSISKAITYK GREITAI
Parsisiųskite BALTIC PETROLEUM mobiliąją programėlę. Saugiai ir greitai atsiskaitykite už degalus automobilyje.  

SPECIALI MANO KAINA
Programėlėje matysite artimiausioje BALTIC PETROLEUM degalinėje specialiai Jums siūlomą degalų kainą.
 
ATSISKAITYK UŽ DEGALUS BE EILĖS
Pasirinkite kolonėlės numerį, kurioje pylėtės degalų;
Spauskite „Apmokėti“.
 
AUTOMATINĖS PLOVYKLOS PASLAUGOS PROGRAMĖLĖJE
Spauskite „Automatinė plovykla“;
Pasirinkite norimą įsigyti plovimo programą;
Braukite į dešinę apmokėjimui;
Plaukite dabar arba plaukite vėliau bet kurioje Baltic Petroleum automatinėje plovykloje.

SAVITARNOS PLOVYKLOS PASLAUGOS PROGRAMĖLĖJE
Spauskite „Savitarnos plovykla“;
Pasirinkite plovyklos boksą, kuriame plausite automobilį;
Pasirinkite sumą ir braukite į dešinę apmokėjimui;
Po sėkmingo apmokėjimo pradėkite plauti automobilį.

SAVITARNOS SIURBLIŲ PASLAUGOS PROGRAMĖLĖJE
Spauskite „Siurblys/Oras“;
Pasirinkite siurblio numerį;
Pasirinkite sumą ir braukite į dešinę apmokėjimui;
Po sėkmingo apmokėjimo pradėkite siurbti automobilį.

MOKĖK KASOJE
Kasoje pasakykite kolonėlės numerį ir/arba paduokite prekes;
Programėlėje paspauskite „Mokėti kasoje“
Pasirinkite kaip atsiskaitysite: Programėlėje pridėta bako kortele arba Grynais/banko kortele
Pateikite QR kodą.
 
DEGALINIŲ ŽEMĖLAPIS
Programėlėje integruotas žemėlapis padės greitai ir patogiai rasti artimiausią BALTIC PETROLEUM degalinę ir  informaciją apie joje teikiamas paslaugas, degalų rūšis bei darbo laiką.
 
PIRKIMŲ ISTORIJA
Mobiliojoje programėlėje visada rasite savo pirkimų istoriją kur ir kiek pylėtės degalų ar pirkote prekių.
 
ATSILIEPIMAI
Mielai atsakysime į Jums rūpimus klausimus. 
Patenkinti klientų lūkesčiai mums svarbiausia. 
Mūsų siekis tapti patikimu Jūsų kelionės partneriu.

Smart-ID is the easiest, most convenient and safest way to authenticate yourself online – check your online bank account, access e-services and confirm transactions.

Smart-ID allows you to give signatures equal to handwritten signatures (except Basic level), which complies with EU regulations about qualified electronic signatures.

Smart-ID is currently available for:
-	Estonian, Latvian, Lithuanian residents
-	Estonian e-residents
-	Belgium residents


EASY 
Get started by downloading Smart-ID app.

Follow the steps in the app to confirm your identity and complete the registration process. Once you’ve done that, you’re good to go – no other confirmation needed! 

CONVENIENT
Your Smart-ID is always within an easy reach!

You can use Smart-ID in as many smart devices as you want and gain access to your online accounts across all of them any time, any place. Using Smart-ID is free and totally unlimited.

SAFE

Smart-ID app does not store your identity or PIN codes. The app is used for key management: it creates your private keys while account registration and later mediates authentication and signature requests. User identity is managed securely by the service provider. A technology has been used in this product for which Cybernetica AS has filed a patent application or a patent has been granted.

Try out Smart-ID, visit portal.smart-id.com!

UPGRADE YOUR FREE ACCOUNT TO ZOOM WORKPLACE PRO AND GET AI COMPANION INCLUDED 
Host unlimited meetings up to 30 hours each

Your Zoom Workplace Pro subscription will automatically renew unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the free trial or the plan billing period. After you start your subscription, you can manage it from either App Store settings or iOS settings. The amount charged to the payment method in your App Store account will vary by the plan you select and your country. The plan price will be displayed before you start your free trial or confirm your purchase.

Follow us on social media @zoom

H2AUTO - išpuoselėtas plovimas kiekvienam iš pirmo karto ir visoms transporto priemonėms.
Su H2AUTO programėle galite aktyvuoti visas paslaugas, už jas atsiskaityti mokėjimo kortele ir sutaupyti su nuolaidų planu.
Kaip tai veikia?
• Atsisiųskite H2AUTO programėlę ir registruokitės: reikalingas jūsų telefono numeris ir mokėjimo kortelė.
• Esant plovykloje aktyvuokite plovimą ar vidaus priežiūros aparatą renkantis iš sąrašą ar skanuojant QR kodą.
• Valdykite plovimą per plovyklos bokse esantį pultą, o vidaus priežiūros aparatų paslaugas rinkitės spaudžiant mygtukus ant aparatų.
• Stabdykite paslaugas arba programėle, arba plovimo pultu.
• Mokėkite tik už laiką, kol naudojotės paslaugomis: programėlė pateiks ataskaitą ir automatiškai nuskaitys pinigus nuo mokėjimo kortelės.
Sutaupykite su nuolaidų planu ir didžiuokites profesionalumu jūsų rankose.
H2AUTO – Viskas nuplauta!

Nova Poshta is a logistics company that quickly and reliably delivers documents, parcels, and cargo anywhere within Ukraine and abroad.

Download the Nova Poshta mobile app and manage your parcels delivery on your smartphone. 

ALL YOUR PACKAGES ARE AT YOUR FINGERTIPS
Convenient parcel sorting on the home screen, statuses, and filters make it easy to find your parcels quickly.

SIMPLE PACKAGES TRACKING AND MANAGEMENT
All the details of your parcel movement are on your smartphone. Quickly and easily check the status of your parcels and order additional services: "Forwarding" and "Other recipient" if your plans have changed and it is inconvenient to receive them at the selected branch or post office, "Return", etc.

COURIER DELIVERY TO AN ADDRESS IN UKRAINE
Now you always know when to expect a courier. The mobile app displays the date and time of their arrival. You can also track their movement on the map, receive an alert 15 minutes before arrival, and chat and call the courier to clarify delivery information.
A large and heavy parcels? Order "Door-to-Door" delivery or "Send From Door" delivery in the app. If your plans change, you can change the date and time of the courier's arrival in one click.

EVEN EASIER TO CREATE A SHIPMENT
Create and track parcels in Ukraine and abroad in the mobile app. Easily track and manage your parcels online when it's on the move.

PAYMENTS AND MONEY TRANSFERS
Create shipments with money transfers in the mobile app and get money in a convenient way - to a bank card or in cash - at any Nova Poshta branch. Pay for parcels in a few taps.

MAP AND NAVIGATION
Easily and conveniently find the right branch or post office on the map in the mobile app.

NP SHOPPING
Shopping with Nova Poshta: delivery to Ukraine from online stores from around the world. Choose your favourite online stores and products, make purchases, pay conveniently, and receive your order at the nearest post office. Buying and delivering your favourite products is now even more affordable.

Kas yra LT ID?

LT ID aplikacija yra skirta nustatyti asmens tapatybę elektroninėje erdvėje ir saugiai pasirašyti dokumentus nuotoliniu kvalifikuotu elektroniniu parašu ar spaudu.

Kodėl LT ID? 

Lengviau prisijungti:
Prisijunkite prie elektroninių sistemų tiesiog įvedę PIN kodą išmaniajame įrenginyje.

Greičiau pasirašyti:
Taupykite laiką vienu paspaudimu patvirtindami didelį kiekį dokumentų.

Lengviau tvirtinti:
Patogiai naudokitės kvalifikuoto el. spaudo sprendimu ir užtikrinkite įmonės dokumentų juridinę galią bei integralumą.

Kaip veikia LT ID?

Atsisiųskite programėlę:
Atsisiųskite ir įdiekite LT ID programėlę savo išmaniajame įrenginyje arba kompiuteryje.

Susiekite įrenginį su paskyra:
Sulaukus pranešimo apie išduotą nuotolinį kvalifikuotą el. parašą ar el. spaudą, atlikite veiksmus, nurodytus LT ID programėlėje ir registruokite įrenginį.

Pradėkite naudotis:
Norėdami prisijungti prie elektroninių sistemų arba pasirašyti dokumentus, pasirinkite LT ID parašą, įveskite savo asmens kodą ir patvirtinkite asmens tapatybę / pasirašymą susikurtu PIN kodu.

Norėdami patvirtinti dokumentus LT ID spaudu, nurodykite savo asmens kodą ir juridinio asmens kodą bei patvirtinkite spaudavimą susikurtu PIN kodu.

Shopify has everything you need to start selling online, for any ecommerce business. Start your business today on the one platform with the ecommerce and point of sale features to start, run, and grow your business.

About this app

Everything you love about WhatsApp plus built-in tools for business
WhatsApp Business is a free-to-download app with built-in tools to help you work smarter, build trust, and grow your business. 

You get  free calls* and free international messaging* plus business features to help you do more with conversations.

Download the app to get business benefits like these:

• Work smarter. Save time by letting the app do the work for you! Send customers automated quick replies and away messages so you never miss an opportunity. Use labels to quickly organize, filter, and find important conversations. Create a status to share an offer or news, and even take orders and payments** in-app to create a great customer experience. 


• Build relationships and trust. With a professional business profile on a secure platform,  you build credibility and trust with customers. Use the app to provide more responsive customer support and build long-term loyalty. Subscribe to Meta Verified*** to reinforce your authenticity.


• Sell more and grow. Get discovered, advertise, and make more valuable customer connections. Boost sales by sending targeted offers to customers; create ads that click to WhatsApp; showcase your product catalog; and give customers the convenience of in-app orders and payments.**

FAQs
Are all features free?
The app is free to download and use, with a mix of free and paid features.

Can I still use my personal WhatsApp?
Yes! As long as you have two different phone numbers, your business and personal accounts can live together on a single device.  

Can I transfer over my chat history?
Yes. When you set up the WhatsApp Business app, you can restore a backup from your WhatsApp account to transfer your messages, media, and contacts to your business account.

How many devices can I connect?
You can have a total of five web-based devices or mobile phones on your account (up to 10 if you subscribe to Meta Verified***). 

*Data charges may apply. Contact your provider for details.
**Not available in all markets
***Available soon globally

Slack brings team communication and collaboration into one place so you can get more work done, whether you belong to a large enterprise or a small business. Slack is available on any device, so you can find and access your team and your work whether you’re at your desk or on the go.
 
Use Slack to: 
 • Communicate with your team and organise your conversations by topic, project or anything else that matters to your work

 • Share and edit documents and collaborate with the right people, all in Slack

Scientifically proven (or at least rumoured) to make your working life simpler, more pleasant and more productive. We hope you’ll give Slack a try.

eTaskulla lähetät yrityksen kuitit ja matkalaskut sähköisesti kirjanpitäjällesi. Helposti, nopeasti ja turvallisesti! Jo yli 20 000 eri kokoista yritystä ja 50% Suomen tilitoimistoista luottaa eTaskuun.

Miksi eTasku?
1. Ei enään hukattuja kuitteja tai tekemättä jääneitä matkalaskuja.
2. Keskity oleelliseen. Yritys ei voi laskuttaa ketään omien tositteidensa toimittamisesta. Siksi se kannattaa tehdä itselle mahdollisimman helpoksi.
3. Säästä aikaa ja hermojasi. Eroon paperista, skannauksesta ja postituksesta. Yhden paperitositteen käsittely vie perinteiseen tapaan noin 6-8 minuuttia. eTaskulla tuo aika vähintään puolittuu!
4. Oikeasti helppokäyttöinen mobiilisovellus. Kuvaa kuitit ja koostat matkalaskut käden käänteessä. Tallennuksen jälkeen ne siirtyvät automaattisesti kirjanpitäjän käsiteltäväksi.

Tärkeimpiä ominaisuuksia eTaskussa:
- Tositteiden kuvaaminen, tallentaminen ja lisätietojen täyttäminen.
- Tositteiden automaattinen lähetys kirjanpitäjälle.
- Matkalaskun koostaminen: Kilometrikorvaukset ja päivärahat (koti-ja ulkomaan).
- Matkalaskun automaattinen lähetys tilitoimistoon kirjanpitäjälle.
- Aineiston varmuuskopiointi ja arkistointi.
- Viestien lähettäminen ja vastaanottaminen käyttäjän ja kirjanpitäjän välillä.
- Mahdollisuus hyväksymiskiertoon.
- Mahdollisuus eKuittien vastaanottoon.
- Dokumenttiarkisto

Tämä sovellus mahdollistaa eTasku -palvelun mobiilikäytön. Sovelluksen avulla voit tallentaa tositteesi eTaskun -pilvipalveluun, jossa ne varmuuskopioituvat automaattisesti ja siirtyvät kirjanpitäjäsi nähtäväille.

Jos tilitoimistosi ei vielä käytä eTaskua, ei hätää, voit käyttää eTaskua myös yksityiskäyttäjänä tai voit tehdä kirjanpitäjällesi maksuttomat tunnukset kirjautumisesi jälkeen.

Huom! Sovelluksen käyttäminen vaatii maksullisen eTasku -käyttäjätunnuksen.

Whova is an award-winning event and conference app. It helps you gain insights about people you meet at events. Whova is one of the most widely used mobile apps by professionals for networking at conferences, trade shows, expos, summits, conventions, business meetings, corporate events, association events, and community gatherings. Whova, the Mobile Event App, has received the Event Technology Awards for five years in a row (2016-2021). 

Watch this PREVIEW VIDEO to see how Whova can help you: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9IKTYK8ZS9g

What makes Whova special? Whova's technology builds comprehensive profiles of attendees so you can view all attendee profiles before you even arrive at the event or conference. Plan in advance whom to meet at an event, what to talk about with each attendee and reach out to others via in-app messages before, during and after the event. You can also create casual meetups and arrange social activities with other groups of attendees. Whova revolutionizes event networking and significantly improves the ROI of attending events.

You can also use the Whova conference app to digitize and manage business cards you receive at events. Whova exceeds other business card reader apps like CamCard, CardMunch, ScanBizCards or Scannable etc. by automatically building full profiles using Whova's SmartProfile technology. This allows you to gain deep insights into your contacts' professional backgrounds, work experience, passions, and interests. Okta Verify is a lightweight app that is used for 2-step verification so you can confirm your identity when you sign in to your Okta account. This gives you an extra layer of security so that you - and only you - can access your applications.

When you sign in to Okta, you can use Okta Verify to obtain a temporary 6-digit code or to approve a request notification sent to your device (your organization must enable notifications to use this feature).

Okta values your privacy. Okta Verify does not store personal information - we request permission only for your device camera, which is used to scan a QR code to register your device with Okta.


App Features

* Enroll in Okta Verify as a new user by registering your mobile device with your Okta account.
* Add one or more Okta accounts that require Okta Verify for authentication.
* Manage 2-factor authentication for non-Okta applications and web services that require the use of passcodes.
* Approve or deny sign-in requests on your device from a push notification (if enabled).


For more information, check out our docs at:
https://help.okta.com/en/prod/okta_help_CSH.htm#ext_okta_verify
